<TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=120 BGCOLOR="#DDDDDD"><FONT CLASS=GraphicCaption>While players are upset about the skill nerf, Oogla here is crying because literally every player has disabled her new Luclin model.</FONT></TD>
<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><IMG SRC="images/spacer.gif"></TD>
